<font face="Impress BT" size="55">Stop joking or I'll kick your ass!</font>

96
00:06:07,730 --> 00:06:09,180
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">I don't mind if you do.</font>

97
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:19,480
