121
00:07:58,130 --> 00:08:02,640
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The shadow holds both the personality and fighting skills of its owner.</font>

122
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:06,900
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">The physical strength of the marionette is limited by the power of it's body.</font>

123
00:08:06,900 --> 00:08:12,270
