<font face="Impress BT" size="55">They were after us from the start.</font>

127
00:08:22,430 --> 00:08:24,690
<font face="Impress BT" size="55">So that's the whole story of Thriller Bark.</font>

128
00:08:24,690 --> 00:08:29,820
